    public class CustomMultiblockBracketHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements crafttweaker.zenscript.IBracketHandler
    A bracket handler for getting a custom multiblock.

    Usage:

    To get by metadata: <multiblock:{meta}>

    To get by resource location: <multiblock:{location}>
